Description:
A variant of nanosleep that takes a 'double' argument and handles EINTR.

Files:
lib/xnanosleep.h
lib/xnanosleep.c
m4/xnanosleep.m4

Depends-on:
c99
dtotimespec
intprops
nanosleep
time
unistd

configure.ac:
gl_XNANOSLEEP

Makefile.am:
lib_SOURCES += xnanosleep.c

Include:
"xnanosleep.h"

Link:
$(LIB_NANOSLEEP)

License:
GPL

Maintainer:
Paul Eggert, Jim Meyering
